---
---

<section id="case-study" class="section-padding bg-gradient-to-b from-dark-50 to-white">
  <div class="container-custom space-y-16">
    <div class="text-center space-y-4">
      <h2 class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-display font-bold">
        Risultati <span class="gradient-text">Documentati</span>
      </h2>
      <p class="text-xl text-dark-400 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
        Veri dati di lanci milionari. Nessun giro di parole. Numeri certificati.
      </p>
    </div>

    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
      <!-- Case Study 1 -->
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-primary-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <div class="flex gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
            RR
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-dark-900">Roberto Re</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Leadership School</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">Fatturato Lancio</p>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-900">€460.320</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">MER</p>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-500">24.78x</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">Giorni</p>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-dark-900">41</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-600 border-t border-dark-100 pt-4">
            "MarketX mi ha aiutato a gestire un lancio complesso con precisione matematica. Risultati oltre le aspettative."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case Study 2 -->
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-primary-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <div class="flex gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-accent-orange to-yellow-600 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
            MP
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-dark-900">Marco Postiglione</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Biutop University</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">Fatturato Lancio</p>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-900">€828.750</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">MER</p>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-500">18.20x</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">Giorni</p>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-dark-900">59</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-600 border-t border-dark-100 pt-4">
            "L'approccio sistematico di MarketX trasforma il caos dei lanci in prevedibilità. Abbiamo replicato 3 volte questo risultato."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Case Study 3 -->
      <div class="bg-white border-2 border-primary-200 rounded-2xl p-8 hover:shadow-2xl transition-all">
        <div class="flex gap-4 mb-6">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-gradient-to-br from-primary-500 to-primary-700 rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-white font-bold text-xl">
            MF
          </div>
          <div>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-dark-900">Massimo Filippi</h3>
            <p class="text-dark-400 text-sm">Biohacking Campus</p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="space-y-4">
          <div class="space-y-2">
            <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">Fatturato Lancio</p>
            <p class="text-3xl font-bold text-dark-900">€304.700</p>
          </div>
          <div class="flex gap-8">
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">MER</p>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-primary-500">14.63x</p>
            </div>
            <div>
              <p class="text-sm text-dark-400">Giorni</p>
              <p class="text-xl font-bold text-dark-900">27</p>
            </div>
          </div>
          <p class="text-sm text-dark-600 border-t border-dark-100 pt-4">
            "In 27 giorni abbiamo fatto quello che altri avrebbero fatto in 6 mesi. La velocità di MarketX è ineguagliabile."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="mt-16 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-600 to-primary-700 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white text-center">
      <h3 class="text-2xl md:text-3xl font-display font-bold mb-4">
        Sono Numeri Reali.
      </h3>
      <p class="text-lg mb-6">
        Nessuno dei nostri case study è finto. Tutti verificabili. Tutti ripetibili.
      </p>
      <p class="text-primary-100">
        "I tuoi guru sono i miei clienti" — Mario Olivelli
      </p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .dark-50 {
    background-color: #f9f9f9;
  }
</style>
